  "description": "A breathtaking aerial view showcases a vibrant sunset over a sea of rolling clouds. The sun, a brilliant orange orb, dominates the upper portion of the image, radiating warmth and light. Below, the landscape is completely obscured by a thick, textured layer of clouds, resembling a vast, undulating ocean. The clouds are illuminated by the setting sun, creating a warm, golden hue across the entire scene. The horizon line is barely visible, lost within the cloud cover, emphasizing the boundless expanse of the sky and the dreamlike quality of the view.",
